</script></center></figure></col_li><col_li environment="col_ol" chapter_type="" wbtag="col_li" xmlns="http://www.math.cuhk.edu.hk/~pschan/cranach"><paragraphs environment="col_ol" chapter_type="" wbtag="paragraphs"> The intersection of each pair of planes is a line and
three such lines are parallel to each other. </paragraphs><figure environment="figure" chapter_type="" wbtag="figure" type="Figure" num="7" md5="a2d67bb1732a5969636180f5df2b6042"><caption environment="figure" chapter_type=""/><center xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" environment="center"><script type="text/tikz" environment="center">
\begin{tikzpicture}[rotate=0,scale=1,arrow/.style={-&gt;,&gt;=stealth,thick}]
